[00:11.53] Over hills
[00:14.18] Green as the springtime,
[00:16.75] Chasing a lonely cloud,
[00:19.34] White as snow
[00:21.90] Some day soon, I mean to catch it,
[00:26.89] Hold tight, and up into the sky I'll go
[00:32.52] I think of what you told me
[00:37.58] However sad life seems
[00:41.85] That sometimes tears
[00:44.22] Can turn to dreams
[00:47.91] If I could only be with you once more,
[00:54.12] And hold you tightly to my heart
[00:58.99] We could walk this road together,
[01:04.57] And never, ever be apart
[01:10.05] Each and every heart will be healed,
