[02:04.64] The call of hope,
[02:07.18] May yet resound
[02:10.92] I close my eyes,
[02:13.66] And you are here,
[02:16.86] Your smiling face shines down on me
[02:21.62] I am alone, but never lonely,
[02:26.85] You're by my side,
[02:28.65] And I can clearly see
