[02:37.08] My mind is clear,
[02:39.65] My heart is strong
[03:07.99] If I could only be with you once more,
[03:13.32] And hold you tightly to my heart
[03:18.34] We could walk this road together,
[03:23.68] And never, ever be apart
[03:28.35] Your light will shine on every forest and field,
[03:33.63] On our journey through another world